title: Elderwood Quinn. (Holy F, is this amazing!)
body:
This picture was created by Chris Sanchez, so go a give him some love.
https://cdnb.artstation.com/p/assets/images/images/009/163/239/large/chris-sanchez-sanchezchris-elderwoodquinn.jpg?1517463410

I just wanted to share his work and say "Hey, Riot. If you need someone to make a concept for a Quinn skin ask this guy." Cause damn, do I like this.

replies.body: Great artwork, but meh skin imo.
Looks a bit too bulky to me but I could get behind it.

> [{quoted}](name=ImGoodAtFeeding,realm=NA,application-id=A8FQeEA8,discussion-id=xVjsm8ja,comment-id=0004,timestamp=2018-02-23T07:12:27.186+0000)
>
> Who?

Love the name BTW, the picture was created by Chris Sanchez. This m8 should be on the production team if Riot was thinking of giving Quinn a skin. Because his art is beautiful, and I think he can come up with much more than just Elderwood Quinn.
Holy crap that artwork is golden. A+~
